column4: U.S. rejects Tesla bid for tariff exemption for Autopilot 'brain'
column5: WASHINGTON U.S. trade officials rejected Tesla Inc's bid for relief from President Donald Trump's 25-percent tariffs on the Chinese-made Autopilot "brain" of its Model 3 and other electric vehicles  one of more than 1 000 product denials linked to China's industrial development plans.

column4: UPDATE 4-U.S. rejects Tesla bid for tariff exemption for Autopilot 'brain'
column5: WASHINGTON  May 3 U.S. trade officials rejected Tesla Inc's bid for relief from President Donald Trump's 25-percent tariffs on the Chinese-made Autopilot "brain" of its Model 3 and other electric vehicles  one of more than 1 000 product denials linked to China's industrial development plans.
